urlText: Moore Park lift out of service
content:
The lift on the Anzac Parade side of the Moore Park light rail stop is not operating.
  • Do not use even if the doors open.
  • Use the pedestrian crossing at the Lang Road traffic lights as an alternative to access the stop or Sydney Cricket Ground.
  • While the lift on the Sydney Cricket Ground is still working, only stairs are available to exit the footbridge on Anzac Parade side.
  • Do not use this lift if you require a lift to exit the footbridge.
subtitle: Moore Park lift out of service

properties.smsText: Moore Park lift out of service
properties.speechText: The lift on the Anzac Parade side of the Moore Park light rail stop is not operating. Do not use even if the doors open.
